Set the env variables: 

CG_DOXYGEN : location of cg src for doxygen
CGDOC_DOXYGEN : location of doxygen config file

setenv CG_DOXYGEN "/home/henshaw.0/cg"
setenv CGDOC_DOXYGEN "/home/henshaw.0/cgDoc/doxygen"

To build an initial config file:
doxygen -g cgDoxygen.config


To build the doxygen source: 
doxygen cgDoxygen.config
